{"type":"answer","id":18502,"parentType":"question","parentId":4096,"uid":2356,"contents":"中华民国道路交通管理处罚条例 (民国75年)<br>\n<br>\n第十一条<br>\n<ul><li>　　<b>军用车辆</b>及军用车辆驾驶人，应遵守本条例有关道路交通管理之规定，并<b>服从执行交通勤务之警察及宪兵指挥。</b></li><li>　　国军编制内之军用车辆及军用车辆驾驶人，违反前项规定之处罚，由国防部定之。</li></ul><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069043561037.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069043561037.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069043561037.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n看来中华民国政府还是要好好学习一个啊，这是坠吼的嚣张！<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069111229112.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069111229112.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069111229112.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-11-02","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}